# Journal Model
class JournalModel(models.Model):
    # Journal Status
    RATING = ((1,'Very High'),(2,'High'),(3,'Normal'),(4,'Low'),(5,'Very Low'))

    # Primary Key
    journal_id = models.UUIDField(primary_key=True, default=uuid.uuid4, editable=False)

    # Inside Serializers
    shop = models.ForeignKey(ShopModel ,on_delete=models.CASCADE)
    machine = models.ForeignKey(MachineModel ,on_delete=models.CASCADE, blank=True, null=True)

    # Active Fields
    journal_comment = models.CharField(max_length=1000, blank=True, null=True)
    journal_rating = models.PositiveSmallIntegerField(choices=RATING,null=True)
    follow_up = models.DateTimeField(null=True, blank=True)

    # Auto add Fields
    time_stamp = models.DateTimeField(auto_now_add=True)
    
    class Meta:
            verbose_name = "Journal Model"
    def __str__(self):
        return self.shop.shop_name + ' - ' + self.journal_comment
